{"tid":985420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣軍隊實彈射擊後解放軍隨即於抖音釋出武嚇影片","createTime":"2019-01-17T14:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:13:33.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c10a88fbbcf044c2ff5d42b2f00e200974d6bc17","tid":985420,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpnenqKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpnenqKQ.jpg&h=e3b82dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國軍今晨貼出雷霆2000火箭擊發影片（右）；中國軍方隨後釋出直升機射擊演練、「祖國必然統一」影片（左）。（左圖取自中國人民陸軍抖音，右圖取自國防部發言人臉書）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕國軍今（17）日清晨在大甲溪口進行實彈射擊，上午8點在臉書貼出雷霆2000火箭擊發影片，獲得網友大力讚賞；不料中國人民解放軍中午馬上跟著釋出模擬作戰影片，簡直像是在與我軍叫陣。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍透過「抖音」帳號「人民陸軍」公布武嚇影片，片中攻擊型直升機在水面上瞄準空中移動飛靶，再成功擊落，接著再展示遙測鏡頭觀測2艘水面上的靶船，攻擊型直升機發射武器，相繼炸毀目標，不過直升機瞄準、發射和命中目標的畫面都經過剪接；這影片背景還配上搖滾風格的音樂，影片末還打上「祖國必然統一」字樣，針對性質濃厚。<br />\n<br />\n影片被轉貼至中國臉書社團「帝吧中央集團軍」，引起中國網友注意，經查證，台灣抖音用戶因手機國家設定，即使有下載「抖音」app也無法查看所有中國用戶發表的貼文，iOS必須將國家切換成中國並同意遵守中國法律才可查看，Android用戶則需藉由中國APP下載程式，下載中國版的抖音才可翻入牆內。<br />\n<br />\n許多台灣網友看見人民解放軍影片後，均感到與我軍盛況相比簡直不值一提，也有網友認為中國的武力嚇阻手法已對台灣人民完全沒有作用，更有人認為，中國軍方選在我軍操演後釋出影片，挑釁意味濃厚，但網友們均同意台灣軍演內容較中國更為震撼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2675036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2675036&d=IXeaUj7MBsH%2FpAjUoWaQHG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1f4be74a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2675036&h=c3a24859\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2675036</a>"},{"pid":"368e9b11f91ac69ebad860d7ee35799982dba328","tid":985420,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:32:19.000Z","msg":"抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2e62097a8ec7fde96ab8a163a0ba0a1ee7eb9b","tid":985420,"uid":9394,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:33:18.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n中國同抖音一樣可笑"},{"pid":"4c9bc3387ed5830ed300bce2aef19b9d0d5fbe2b","tid":985420,"uid":7916,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"進化到抖音攻台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0f103332bed43ed85fa5cbf4c37051353d25e6","tid":985420,"uid":51720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"「阿Q」型應用程式 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe29460206a2c57652c5e4bad4c0ba447d109ed","tid":985420,"uid":150347,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFGW6ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFGW6ja.gif&h=bfbc4b2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4307242da056f0d5f6ff0f7b00c0fb20b9907668","tid":985420,"uid":100029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abe29460206a2c57652c5e4bad4c0ba447d109ed","tid":985420,"uid":150347,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFGW6ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFGW6ja.gif&h=bfbc4b2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T04:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9543f4a545f1de3fef9f6fcc75412b02774d9e","tid":985420,"uid":82929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c9bc3387ed5830ed300bce2aef19b9d0d5fbe2b","tid":985420,"uid":7916,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"進化到抖音攻台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\